[
  {
    "bookname": "Amos",
    "chapter": "9",
    "text": "<p class=\"bodytext\">I <st data-num=\"07200\" class=\"\">saw</st> the <st data-num=\"0136\" class=\"\">Lord</st><n id=\"1\" /> <st data-num=\"05324\" class=\"\">standing</st> <st data-num=\"05921\" class=\"\">by</st> the <st data-num=\"04196\" class=\"\">altar</st><n id=\"2\" /> and he <st data-num=\"0559\" class=\"\">said</st>, <p class=\"poetry\">\u201c<st data-num=\"05221\" class=\"\">Strike</st> the <st data-num=\"03730\" class=\"\">tops of the support pillars</st>,<n id=\"3\" /> so the <st data-num=\"05592\" class=\"\">thresholds</st> <st data-num=\"07493\" class=\"\">shake</st>!<p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"01214\" class=\"\">Knock</st> them <st data-num=\"01214\" class=\"\">down</st> on the <st data-num=\"07218\" class=\"\">heads</st> of <st data-num=\"03605\" class=\"\">all</st> the people,<n id=\"4\" /> <p class=\"poetry\">and I will <st data-num=\"02026\" class=\"\">kill</st> the <st data-num=\"0319\" class=\"\">survivors</st><n id=\"5\" /> with the <st data-num=\"02719\" class=\"\">sword</st>.<p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"03808\" class=\"\">No</st> <st data-num=\"05127\" class=\"\">one</st> will be able to <st data-num=\"05127\" class=\"\">run away</st>;<n id=\"6\" /> <p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"03808\" class=\"\">no</st> <st data-num=\"06412\" class=\"\">one</st> will be able to <st data-num=\"04422\" class=\"\">escape</st>.<n id=\"7\" /> </p>",
    "verse": "1"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Amos",
    "chapter": "9",
    "text": "<p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"0518\" class=\"\">Even if</st> they could <st data-num=\"02864\" class=\"\">dig down</st> into the <st data-num=\"07585\" class=\"\">netherworld</st>,<n id=\"1\" /> <p class=\"poetry\">my <st data-num=\"03027\" class=\"\">hand</st> would <st data-num=\"03947\" class=\"\">pull</st> them <st data-num=\"03947\" class=\"\">up</st> from <st data-num=\"08033\" class=\"\">there</st>.<p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"0518\" class=\"\">Even if</st> they could <st data-num=\"05927\" class=\"\">climb up</st> to <st data-num=\"08064\" class=\"\">heaven</st>,<p class=\"poetry\">I would <st data-num=\"03381\" class=\"\">drag</st> them <st data-num=\"03381\" class=\"\">down</st> from <st data-num=\"08033\" class=\"\">there</st>. </p>",
    "verse": "2"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Amos",
    "chapter": "9",
    "text": "<p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"0518\" class=\"\">Even if</st> they were to <st data-num=\"02244\" class=\"\">hide</st> on the <st data-num=\"07218\" class=\"\">top</st> of <st data-num=\"03760\">Mount Carmel</st>,<p class=\"poetry\">I would <st data-num=\"02664\" class=\"\">hunt</st> them <st data-num=\"02664\" class=\"\">down</st> and <st data-num=\"03947\" class=\"\">take</st> them from <st data-num=\"08033\" class=\"\">there</st>.<p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"0518\" class=\"\">Even if</st> they tried to <st data-num=\"05641\" class=\"\">hide</st> <st data-num=\"05048\" class=\"\">from</st> <st data-num=\"05869\" class=\"\">me</st><n id=\"1\" /> at the <st data-num=\"07172\" class=\"\">bottom</st> of the <st data-num=\"03220\" class=\"\">sea</st>,<p class=\"poetry\">from <st data-num=\"08033\" class=\"\">there</st><n id=\"2\" /> I would <st data-num=\"06680\" class=\"\">command</st> the <st data-num=\"05175\" class=\"\">Sea Serpent</st><n id=\"3\" /> to <st data-num=\"05391\" class=\"\">bite</st> them.</p>",
    "verse": "3"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Amos",
    "chapter": "9",
    "text": "<p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"0518\" class=\"\">Even when</st> their <st data-num=\"0341\" class=\"\">enemies</st> <st data-num=\"01980 06440\">drive</st> them into <st data-num=\"07628\" class=\"\">captivity</st>,<n id=\"1\" /> <p class=\"poetry\">from <st data-num=\"08033\" class=\"\">there</st><n id=\"2\" /> I will <st data-num=\"06680\" class=\"\">command</st> the <st data-num=\"02719\" class=\"\">sword</st> to <st data-num=\"02026\" class=\"\">kill</st> them.<p class=\"poetry\">I will <st data-num=\"07760 05921\">not let</st> them <st data-num=\"07760 05921\">out of</st> my <st data-num=\"05869\" class=\"\">sight</st>;<p class=\"poetry\">they will experience <st data-num=\"07451\" class=\"\">disaster</st>, <st data-num=\"03808\" class=\"\">not</st> <st data-num=\"02896\" class=\"\">prosperity</st>.\u201d<n id=\"3\" /> </p>",
    "verse": "4"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Amos",
    "chapter": "9",
    "text": "<p class=\"poetrybreak\">The <st data-num=\"0136\" class=\"\">Sovereign</st> <span class=\"smcaps\"><st data-num=\"03068\">Lord</st></span> of <st data-num=\"06635\" class=\"\">Heaven\u2019s Armies</st> will do this.<n id=\"1\" /> <p class=\"poetry\">He <st data-num=\"05060\" class=\"\">touches</st> the <st data-num=\"0776\" class=\"\">earth</st> and it <st data-num=\"04127\" class=\"\">dissolves</st>;<n id=\"2\" /> <p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"03605\" class=\"\">all</st> who <st data-num=\"03427\" class=\"\">live</st> on it <st data-num=\"056\" class=\"\">mourn</st>.<p class=\"poetry\">The <st data-num=\"03605\" class=\"\">whole</st> earth<n id=\"3\" /> <st data-num=\"05927\" class=\"\">rises</st> like the <st data-num=\"02975\" class=\"\">Nile River</st><n id=\"4\" /> <p class=\"poetry\">and then <st data-num=\"08257\" class=\"\">grows calm</st><n id=\"5\" /> like the <st data-num=\"02975\" class=\"\">Nile</st> in <st data-num=\"04714\" class=\"\">Egypt</st>.<n id=\"6\" /> </p>",
    "verse": "5"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Amos",
    "chapter": "9",
    "text": "<p class=\"poetry\">He <st data-num=\"01129\" class=\"\">builds</st> the <st data-num=\"05944\" class=\"\">upper rooms</st> of his palace<n id=\"1\" /> in <st data-num=\"08064\" class=\"\">heaven</st><p class=\"poetry\">and <st data-num=\"03245\" class=\"\">sets</st> its <st data-num=\"092\" class=\"\">foundation supports</st><n id=\"2\" /> <st data-num=\"05921\" class=\"\">on</st> the <st data-num=\"0776\" class=\"\">earth</st>.<n id=\"3\" /> <p class=\"poetry\">He <st data-num=\"07121\" class=\"\">summons</st> the <st data-num=\"04325\" class=\"\">water</st> of the <st data-num=\"03220\" class=\"\">sea</st><p class=\"poetry\">and <st data-num=\"08210\" class=\"\">pours</st> it <st data-num=\"08210\" class=\"\">out</st> <st data-num=\"05921\" class=\"\">on</st> the <st data-num=\"0776\" class=\"\">earth\u2019s</st> <st data-num=\"06440\" class=\"\">surface</st>.<p class=\"poetry\">The <span class=\"smcaps\"><st data-num=\"03068\" class=\"\">Lord</st></span> is his <st data-num=\"08034\" class=\"\">name</st>. </p>",
    "verse": "6"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Amos",
    "chapter": "9",
    "text": "<p class=\"poetry\">\u201c<st data-num=\"0859\" class=\"\">You</st> <st data-num=\"01121 03478\">Israelites</st> are <st data-num=\"03808\" class=\"\">just</st> like the <st data-num=\"01121 03569\">Ethiopians</st> in my sight,\u201d<n id=\"1\" /> <st data-num=\"05002\" class=\"\">says</st> the <span class=\"smcaps\"><st data-num=\"03068\" class=\"\">Lord</st></span>. <p class=\"poetry\">\u201c<st data-num=\"03808\" class=\"\">Certainly</st> I <st data-num=\"05927\" class=\"\">brought</st> <st data-num=\"03478\" class=\"\">Israel</st> <st data-num=\"05927\" class=\"\">up</st> from the <st data-num=\"0776\" class=\"\">land</st> of <st data-num=\"04714\" class=\"\">Egypt</st>, <p class=\"poetry\">but I also brought the <st data-num=\"06430\" class=\"\">Philistines</st> from <st data-num=\"03731\" class=\"\">Caphtor</st><n id=\"2\" /> and the <st data-num=\"0758\" class=\"\">Arameans</st> from <st data-num=\"07024\" class=\"\">Kir</st>.<n id=\"3\" /> </p>",
    "verse": "7"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Amos",
    "chapter": "9",
    "text": "<p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"02009\" class=\"\">Look</st>, the <st data-num=\"0136\" class=\"\">Sovereign</st> <span class=\"smcaps\"><st data-num=\"03068\" class=\"\">Lord</st></span> is <st data-num=\"05869\" class=\"\">watching</st><n id=\"1\" /> the <st data-num=\"02400\" class=\"\">sinful</st> <st data-num=\"04467\" class=\"\">nation</st>,<n id=\"2\" /> <p class=\"poetry\">and I will <st data-num=\"08045\" class=\"\">destroy</st> it <st data-num=\"05921\" class=\"\">from</st> the <st data-num=\"06440\" class=\"\">face</st> of the <st data-num=\"0127\" class=\"\">earth</st>.<p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"0657 03588\">But</st> I will <st data-num=\"03808\" class=\"\">not</st> <st data-num=\"08045\" class=\"\">completely</st> <st data-num=\"08045\" class=\"\">destroy</st> the <st data-num=\"01004\" class=\"\">family</st><n id=\"3\" /> of <st data-num=\"03290\" class=\"\">Jacob</st>,\u201d <st data-num=\"05002\" class=\"\">says</st> the <span class=\"smcaps\"><st data-num=\"03068\" class=\"\">Lord</st></span>. </p>",
    "verse": "8"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Amos",
    "chapter": "9",
    "text": "<p class=\"poetry\">\u201c<st data-num=\"03588\" class=\"\">For</st> <st data-num=\"02009\" class=\"\">look</st>, <st data-num=\"0595\" class=\"\">I</st> am <st data-num=\"06680\" class=\"\">giving a command</st>,<p class=\"poetry\">and I will <st data-num=\"05128\" class=\"\">shake</st> the <st data-num=\"01004\" class=\"\">family</st> of <st data-num=\"03478\" class=\"\">Israel</st> together with <st data-num=\"03605\" class=\"\">all</st> the <st data-num=\"01471\" class=\"\">nations</st>.<p class=\"poetry\">It will <st data-num=\"0834\" class=\"\">resemble</st> a <st data-num=\"03531\" class=\"\">sieve</st> being <st data-num=\"05128\" class=\"\">shaken</st>, <p class=\"poetry\">when <st data-num=\"03808\" class=\"\">not</st> even a <st data-num=\"06872\" class=\"\">pebble</st> <st data-num=\"05307\" class=\"\">falls</st> to the <st data-num=\"0776\" class=\"\">ground</st>.<n id=\"1\" /> </p>",
    "verse": "9"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Amos",
    "chapter": "9",
    "text": "<p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"03605\" class=\"\">All</st> the <st data-num=\"02400\" class=\"\">sinners</st> among my <st data-num=\"05971\" class=\"\">people</st> will <st data-num=\"04191\" class=\"\">die</st> by the <st data-num=\"02719\" class=\"\">sword</st>\u2014<p class=\"poetry\">the ones who <st data-num=\"0559\" class=\"\">say</st>, \u2018<st data-num=\"07451\" class=\"\">Disaster</st> will <st data-num=\"03808\" class=\"\">not</st> <st data-num=\"05066\" class=\"\">come near</st>, it will not <st data-num=\"06923 05704\">confront</st> us.\u2019</p>",
    "verse": "10"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Amos",
    "chapter": "9",
    "text": "<p class=\"poetry\">\u201cIn <st data-num=\"01931\" class=\"\">that</st> <st data-num=\"03117\" class=\"\">day</st> I will <st data-num=\"06965\" class=\"\">rebuild</st> the <st data-num=\"05307\" class=\"\">collapsing</st> <st data-num=\"05521\" class=\"\">hut</st><n id=\"1\" /> of <st data-num=\"01732\" class=\"\">David</st>.<p class=\"poetry\">I will <st data-num=\"01443\" class=\"\">seal</st> its<n id=\"2\" /> <st data-num=\"06556\" class=\"\">gaps</st>,<p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"06965\" class=\"\">repair</st> its<n id=\"3\" /> <st data-num=\"02034\" class=\"\">ruins</st>,<p class=\"poetry\">and <st data-num=\"01129\" class=\"\">restore</st> it to what it was like in <st data-num=\"03117\" class=\"\">days</st> <st data-num=\"05769\" class=\"\">gone by</st>.<n id=\"4\" /></p>",
    "verse": "11"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Amos",
    "chapter": "9",
    "text": "<p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"04616\" class=\"\">As a result</st> they<n id=\"1\" /> will <st data-num=\"03423\" class=\"\">conquer</st> <st data-num=\"07611\" class=\"\">those left</st> in <st data-num=\"0123\" class=\"\">Edom</st><n id=\"2\" /> <p class=\"poetry\">and <st data-num=\"03605\" class=\"\">all</st> the <st data-num=\"01471\" class=\"\">nations</st> <st data-num=\"0834 07121 05921\">subject to</st> my <st data-num=\"08034\" class=\"\">rule</st>.\u201d<n id=\"3\" /> <p class=\"poetry\">The <span class=\"smcaps\"><st data-num=\"03068\" class=\"\">Lord</st></span>, who is about to <st data-num=\"06213\" class=\"\">do</st> <st data-num=\"02063\" class=\"\">this</st>, is <st data-num=\"05002\" class=\"\">speaking</st>. </p>",
    "verse": "12"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Amos",
    "chapter": "9",
    "text": "<p class=\"poetry\">\u201c<st data-num=\"02009\" class=\"\">Be sure of this</st>,<n id=\"1\" /> the <st data-num=\"03117\" class=\"\">time</st> is<n id=\"2\" /> <st data-num=\"0935\" class=\"\">coming</st>,\u201d <st data-num=\"05002\" class=\"\">says</st> the <span class=\"smcaps\"><st data-num=\"03068\" class=\"\">Lord</st></span>,<p class=\"poetry\">\u201cwhen the <st data-num=\"02790\" class=\"\">plowman</st> will <st data-num=\"05066\" class=\"\">catch up</st> to the <st data-num=\"07114\" class=\"\">reaper</st>,<n id=\"3\" /> <p class=\"poetry\">and the one who <st data-num=\"01869\" class=\"\">stomps</st> the <st data-num=\"06025\" class=\"\">grapes</st><n id=\"4\" /> will overtake<n id=\"5\" /> the <st data-num=\"04900 02233\">planter</st>.<n id=\"6\" /> <p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"06071\" class=\"\">Juice</st> will <st data-num=\"05197\" class=\"\">run down</st> the <st data-num=\"02022\" class=\"\">slopes</st>;<n id=\"7\" /> <p class=\"poetry\">it will <st data-num=\"04127\" class=\"\">flow down</st> <st data-num=\"03605\" class=\"\">all</st> the <st data-num=\"01389\" class=\"\">hillsides</st>.<n id=\"8\" /> </p>",
    "verse": "13"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Amos",
    "chapter": "9",
    "text": "<p class=\"poetry\">I will <st data-num=\"07725\" class=\"\">bring back</st> my <st data-num=\"07622 05971\">people</st>, <st data-num=\"03478\" class=\"\">Israel</st>;<n id=\"1\" /> <p class=\"poetry\">they will <st data-num=\"01129\" class=\"\">rebuild</st> the <st data-num=\"05892\" class=\"\">cities</st> <st data-num=\"08074\" class=\"\">lying in rubble</st><n id=\"2\" /> and <st data-num=\"03427\" class=\"\">settle down</st>.<n id=\"3\" /> <p class=\"poetry\">They will <st data-num=\"05193\" class=\"\">plant</st> <st data-num=\"03754\" class=\"\">vineyards</st> and <st data-num=\"08354\" class=\"\">drink</st> the <st data-num=\"03196\" class=\"\">wine</st> they produce;<n id=\"4\" /> <p class=\"poetry\">they will <st data-num=\"06213\" class=\"\">grow</st> <st data-num=\"01593\" class=\"\">orchards</st><n id=\"5\" /> and <st data-num=\"0398\" class=\"\">eat</st> the <st data-num=\"06529\" class=\"\">fruit</st> they produce.<n id=\"6\" /> </p>",
    "verse": "14"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Amos",
    "chapter": "9",
    "text": "<p class=\"poetry\">I will <st data-num=\"05193\" class=\"\">plant</st> them <st data-num=\"05921\" class=\"\">on</st> their <st data-num=\"0127\" class=\"\">land</st>,<p class=\"poetry\">and they will <st data-num=\"03808\" class=\"\">never</st> <st data-num=\"05750\" class=\"\">again</st> be <st data-num=\"05428\" class=\"\">uprooted</st> <st data-num=\"05921\" class=\"\">from</st> the<n id=\"1\" /> <st data-num=\"0127 0834\">land</st> I have <st data-num=\"05414\" class=\"\">given</st> <st data-num=\"01992\" class=\"\">them</st>,\u201d<p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"0559\" class=\"\">says</st> the <span class=\"smcaps\"><st data-num=\"03068\" class=\"\">Lord</st></span> your <st data-num=\"0430\" class=\"\">God</st>. </p>",
    "verse": "15"
  }
]